# uv and ui

## Assume this project uses `uv`

When cursor runs a command, use `uv add` instead of `pip ...`
When trying to do `python oppman.py`, it should do `uv run python oppman.py`

## UI

Try to use htmx, daisy ui, alpine.js, and tailwindcss when possible.
